OL,4,CTokyo Paralympics: Most of Channel 4's
OL,5,CTV hosts will be disabled
OL,6, More than 70% of Channel 4's presenting
OL,7, team for the Paralympic Games will be
OL,8, disabled, the broadcaster has pledged.
OL,10,FPresenters for the event, which takes
OL,11,Fplace in Tokyo in August and September,
OL,12,Fwill include TV host and former
OL,13,Fbasketball player Ade Adepitan.
OL,15,FHe'll be joined by disability advocate
OL,16,FSophie Morgan, ex-rugby player Ed
OL,17,FJackson and Strictly star JJ Chalmers.
OL,19,FChannel 4 said it would be the largest
OL,20,Fnumber of disabled presenters ever seen
OL,21,Fon UK TV.
